{"tid":2012212,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"如果鼬同四代冇早死，會唔會係全火影最強角色？","createTime":"2020-05-11T13:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T04:34:37.000Z","uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"693e21c88ac3bc02d13637db838259690bc20989","tid":2012212,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"班同柱間細過係勁，但未到四代同鼬咁誇張，直情係神童咁。<br />\n論天分同智商一定係四代鼬最勁，不過可惜早死，未去到全盛期。<br />\n<br />\n雖然鼬唔係六道轉世，但三神器體系仲勁過大筒木體系。<br />\n佢把十拳劍應該可以秒左輝夜姬，八尺鏡可以反彈十尾尾獸玉。<br />\n<br />\n至於四代，比佢好似班咁長命，應該開放好多外掛新忍術。"},{"pid":"dbd2b408ccd7f557ea7b9614179c5ea6296ca8c5","tid":2012212,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"是但"},{"pid":"55d6d6ae20c2328c55180534df39a97d9bcd4e69","tid":2012212,"uid":75050,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/gv4LPGP/w76TpU-0.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Fgv4LPGP%2Fw76TpU-0.jpg%3F&h=d9813f17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ddbb6e4433809f20f1416e00ad85b6142755543","tid":2012212,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:25:09.000Z","msg":"嘴遁"},{"pid":"b0b0eb2c4b57b815568b99c910e956e117937fc2","tid":2012212,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"55d6d6ae20c2328c55180534df39a97d9bcd4e69","tid":2012212,"uid":75050,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/gv4LPGP/w76TpU-0.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Fgv4LPGP%2Fw76TpU-0.jpg%3F&h=d9813f17&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:26:45.000Z","msg":"其實岸本預設左佢有好多勁忍術，只係懶得畫出黎。<br />\n睇戰績，至少佢打嬴全盛大蛇丸。<br />\n同班打的果一屆五影，應該全部唔夠三代火影打"},{"pid":"a293fc4028caed1755af7ae788986f5bde6a133d","tid":2012212,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b0b0eb2c4b57b815568b99c910e